The easiest way
to find Susie
is to go to the police.

43
00:03:23,174 --> 00:03:25,938
Well, where are the police?

44
00:03:26,010 --> 00:03:28,308
Right there.

45
00:03:28,379 --> 00:03:32,110
[Policeman] Right where?
Right down there
under the pier.

46
00:03:32,183 --> 00:03:34,208
