<i><music> With my Lord <music></i>

1884
02:00:14,248 --> 02:00:20,915
<music> Ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh <music>

1885
02:00:20,988 --> 02:00:25,322
<i>"I will lift up mine eyes</i>
<i>unto the hills from whence</i>
<i>cometh my help. </i>

1886
02:00:25,392 --> 02:00:29,590
"My help cometh from the Lord
which made heaven and earth.

1887
02:00:29,663 --> 02:00:32,564
"He will not suffer thy foot
to be moved.

1888
02:00:32,633 --> 02:00:35,932
"He that keepeth thee
will not slumber.

1889
02:00:36,003 --> 02:00:40,406
<i>"Behold, he that keepeth Israel</i>
<i>shall neither slumber</i>
<i>nor sleep. </i>

1890
02:00:40,474 --> 02:00:43,443
<i>"The Lord is thy keeper. </i>

1891
02:00:43,510 --> 02:00:46,502
<i>"The Lord is the shade</i>
<i>upon thy right hand. </i>

1892
02:00:46,580 --> 02:00:49,811
<i>"The sun shall not</i>
<i>smite thee by day... </i>

1893
02:00:49,883 --> 02:00:51,851
<i>"nor the moon by night. </i>

1894
02:00:51,919 --> 02:00:55,855
<i>"The Lord shall preserve thee</i>
<i>from all evil. </i>

1895
02:00:55,923 --> 02:00:58,084
<i>"He shall preserve thy soul. </i>

1896
02:00:58,158 --> 02:01:02,219
<i>The Lord shall preserve</i>
<i>thy going out</i>
<i>and thy coming in. "</i>

1897
02:01:02,296 --> 02:01:05,094
Let me through!
Please!

1898
02:01:05,165 --> 02:01:07,099
Please, let me through!

1899
02:01:11,705 --> 02:01:13,639
[Policeman]
Hey, stand back, miss.

1900
02:01:13,707 --> 02:01:15,971
But it's my mother!
Stand back.

1901
02:01:16,043 --> 02:01:20,139
I'm telling you,
it's my mother!

1902
02:01:20,213 --> 02:01:22,977
Please.
[Crying]

1903
02:01:24,217 --> 02:01:26,742
Mama!

1904
02:01:26,820 --> 02:01:30,085
<i>[Sobbing]</i>
<i>Mama! </i>

1905
02:01:32,392 --> 02:01:34,485
I didn't mean it.

1906
02:01:34,561 --> 02:01:36,529
I didn't mean it.

1907
02:01:36,597 --> 02:01:40,328
[Sobbing Continues]
Mama, do you hear me?

1908
02:01:40,400 --> 02:01:43,267
I'm sorry.

1909
02:01:43,337 --> 02:01:46,397
I'm sorry, Mama.

1910
02:01:46,473 --> 02:01:49,533
Mama, I did love you.
[Sobbing]

1911
02:01:51,111 --> 02:01:54,205
Sarah Jane.
Sarah Jane, don't!

1912
02:01:56,149 --> 02:01:58,083
Miss Lora.

1913
02:01:59,686 --> 02:02:02,280
Miss Lora,
I killed my mother.

1914
02:02:02,356 --> 02:02:04,290
I killed her.

1915
02:02:04,358 --> 02:02:07,122
I wanted to come home.
Shh.

1916
02:02:07,194 --> 02:02:10,960
Now she'll never know how much
I wanted to come home.
Come with us.

1917
02:02:13,400 --> 02:02:15,834
<i>[People Murmuring]</i>

1918
